<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٩١)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" ولد الزِّنَا شَرّ الثَّلَاثَة "</span> أَن ذَلِك فِي رجل مَخْصُوص.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٩٢)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" هلا تَرَكْتُمُوهُ وجئتموني بِهِ "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يَعْنِي ماعزا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٩٣)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" لَا تقطع يَد السَّارِق فِيمَا دون الْمِجَن "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٩٤)</span> وَحَدِيث: <span class="c1">" أَمر بِالرجلَيْنِ وَالْمَرْأَة فَضربُوا حَدهمْ "</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>